{"tid":1385004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何回應屌港鐵不合作運動者","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:46:30.000Z","uid":293580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0496e7733eeb85b54927f61327bae026b6e8cf43","tid":1385004,"uid":293580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"港鐵不合作運動，總有藍藍地或聲稱中立嘅人嘈嘈閉（深藍冇得救，慳返啖氣啦），同事食飯朋友聚會實有㗎啦，如果口痕想贈佢哋兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可以咁樣樣：<br />\n<br />\n1.1 對方為非涉事者：「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又唔影響到你</span></span>，理得佢哋啫。」<br />\n1.2 如果對方冥頑不靈：「咁影響到其他乘客呀嘛！」可以咁答：「咁上水咁多水貨客霸路、平日上落貨搵食車霸晒成條行車線啦，夠影響一般市民，又唔見你咁憤慨？」<br />\n<br />\n2.1 對方為涉事者：「咪好囉，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以拿正牌遲返工</span></span>。」<br />\n2.2 如果對方寧頑不寧：「遲到會畀老細屌㗎！」可以咁答：「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乜你老細咁仆街㗎</span></span>。」等個焦點轉移去其他地方。<br />\n2.3 如果對方寧頑不寧：「咁我好多嘢做㗎嘛！」可以咁答：「咪好囉，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拿正牌可以做唔切</span></span>。」如果對方撻返老細出來，可參考2.2答法。<br />\n<br />\n記得全程<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保持微笑</span></span>，突顯對方lose temper，激動激進。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n在歪理當道的時代，如果道理講不清，不妨換轉角度，歪理vs歪理，要對家正理怪論都輸。"},{"pid":"608e1d0774be11fe42445b2726f9704bcc7d93b0","tid":1385004,"uid":82947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"係咩令到你咁鍾意番工啊 係愛啊 定係責任啊？"},{"pid":"ab37c93525136ca7d4de39bbf4bbaa0c41b7ac5b","tid":1385004,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"岩 唔好屌佢先<br />\n扮聽佢講野，最尾補多句 最衰林鄭搞到人番唔到工 就得<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動不應該有dress code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384645</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eabf385b5cfa76226cecd4f15e085a6e455cdec4","tid":1385004,"uid":293580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"608e1d0774be11fe42445b2726f9704bcc7d93b0","tid":1385004,"uid":82947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"係咩令到你咁鍾意番工啊 係愛啊 定係責任啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"不妨補句，「又真係唔見你平時咁鍾意份工喎。」<br />\n記得保持微笑。"},{"pid":"95fe64f316a20c0180cc5787e988888243655c6b","tid":1385004,"uid":293580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab37c93525136ca7d4de39bbf4bbaa0c41b7ac5b","tid":1385004,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"岩 唔好屌佢先<br />\n扮聽佢講野，最尾補多句 最衰林鄭搞到人番唔到工 就得<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動不應該有dress code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384645</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"呢招正確，總之講講下，追溯源頭，「最衰林鄭」。"},{"pid":"0c7bcdd7da577cdd08973cf5a8df42c67b831ab9","tid":1385004,"uid":82947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab37c93525136ca7d4de39bbf4bbaa0c41b7ac5b","tid":1385004,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"岩 唔好屌佢先<br />\n扮聽佢講野，最尾補多句 最衰林鄭搞到人番唔到工 就得<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動不應該有dress code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384645</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"今日屌曬林鄭同盧蛇<br />\n<br />\n唔俾班後生遊行 咪唯有搞你哋囉"},{"pid":"a4ba6731c0690e2aca89e65e7676d488bfa63ffb","tid":1385004,"uid":293580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c7bcdd7da577cdd08973cf5a8df42c67b831ab9","tid":1385004,"uid":82947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab37c93525136ca7d4de39bbf4bbaa0c41b7ac5b","tid":1385004,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"岩 唔好屌佢先<br />\n扮聽佢講野，最尾補多句 最衰林鄭搞到人番唔到工 就得<br />\n<br />\n不合作運動不應該有dress code<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384645</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"今日屌曬林鄭同盧蛇<br />\n<br />\n唔俾班後生遊行 咪唯有搞你哋囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"其實根本就係要影響到民生呀，<br />\n唔係不合作運動做來把撚咩！"},{"pid":"2a4bbb0c01f7f6f24907dff852d0ad0c262a6500","tid":1385004,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"Spin<br />\n<br />\n屌你地鐵明知今日會有人搞都唔計劃好啲<br />\n平時自己都成日壞啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"2209b9534cf40a5d3d3de240d6bb00cc93ec39f0","tid":1385004,"uid":293580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a4bbb0c01f7f6f24907dff852d0ad0c262a6500","tid":1385004,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"Spin<br />\n<br />\n屌你地鐵明知今日會有人搞都唔計劃好啲<br />\n平時自己都成日壞啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:13:34.000Z","msg":"咪臭係，<br />\n平時日L日都訊號故障，<br />\n夠好不合作啦"},{"pid":"63fa14d3dccea5e866d2b431d8763be238d6fe29","tid":1385004,"uid":72369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"任何一個和平既行動都應該支持<br />\n反少日工 可以減少後生仔係前線流血既機會<br />\n點解唔支持呢？"},{"pid":"d2ea2ed3645593d655896c50efb8becfac03c431","tid":1385004,"uid":293580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"亦都可以咁樣代入對家思維，<br />\n集會遊行示威的時候，政府、建制派、警方咪成日呼籲啲人盡量唔好去現場嘅，否則沙塵滾滾殺錯良民，有咩事唔抵可憐。<br />\n呢個講法基本上完全可以套用落去：<br />\n「咁你明知港鐵有不合作運動，明知啲人阻住地球轉，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁你仲走埋去做乜？</span></span>咁你同示威期期聲稱係居民落街畀差佬逗之後嘈之巴閉有咩分別？」"},{"pid":"481962b16b125acf5afaea3eee8224567f180466","tid":1385004,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"最緊要唔好道歉，做緊公義既事既人絕對唔駛對港奴道歉"}]}